  <brief_title>A Study of the Effects of Probiotics in Children Grades 1-3</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled Study of the Effects of Probiotics in Children Grades 1-3</official_title>
  <sponsors>
