  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to determine the appropriate study design for a
      full-scale claims support study to evaluate the impact of 2 probiotics on healthy days in
      elementary school children relative to a placebo control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
