  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Be in good general health as reported by their parent(s)/legal guardian;

          -  Be willing to refrain from ingesting any product that contains fermented live bacteria
             (other than their test product) during the study as confirmed by their parent(s)/legal
             guardian(s);

          -  Be willing to continue their current dietary habits for the duration of the study as
             confirmed by their parent(s)/legal guardian(s)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Have a known hypersensitivity or allergy to any product ingredient to be ingested
             during the study, as reported by their parent(s)/legal guardian(s)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
